## 💰 Cost Management

### Budgets
- **Daily cap:** $10 USD (soft limit)
- **Per-user session cap:** $2 USD
- **Render/video generation:** $0.50 per request max
- **Budget research:** $0.10 per item (target)

### Cost Tracking
Every AI/API call must log:
- Provider
- Model
- Tokens (input/output)
- Cost (USD)
- Latency
- Success/failure

### Optimization Rules
1. Cache LLM responses where possible (keyed by prompt hash)
2. Use cheaper models for simple tasks (Flash > Pro, Haiku > Sonnet)
3. Batch requests when API supports it
4. Set max_tokens limits to prevent runaway costs

