## 🔒 Security Rules

### API Keys
- ✅ Stored in `.env` (never committed)
- ✅ Accessed via `process.env.XYZ_API_KEY`
- ✅ Rotated quarterly
- ❌ Never logged in plaintext
- ❌ Never sent to client

### User Data
- Minimal data collection
- No PII in telemetry by default
- Project data anonymized in logs
- Clear data retention policy (planned)

### Input Validation
- All user inputs validated with Zod schemas
- SQL injection not applicable (no SQL yet)
- XSS prevented by React escaping
- CORS configured for known origins only

