## 📊 Telemetry Requirements

### Required Events
Every feature must emit:
- `feature_used` (what was used)
- `feature_completed` or `feature_failed`
- `feature_cost` (if involves external APIs)
- `feature_latency`

### Event Schema
```typescript
{
  timestamp: string;       // ISO 8601
  event_type: string;
  agent?: string;
  project_id?: string;
  session_id: string;
  latency_ms: number;
  cost_usd: number;
  provider?: string;
  metadata: Record<string, any>;
}
```

