## 🚫 Anti-Patterns to Avoid

### Code
- ❌ God components (>500 lines)
- ❌ Prop drilling (use Zustand)
- ❌ Mutable state
- ❌ any types
- ❌ Commented-out code (delete it)
- ❌ Console.log in production (use proper logging)

### Architecture
- ❌ Business logic in components
- ❌ Direct API calls from UI (use API layer)
- ❌ Hardcoded URLs/keys
- ❌ Mixing concerns (AI logic in UI code)

### AI Usage
- ❌ Using LLM to calculate simple math
- ❌ No error handling on AI calls
- ❌ No cost tracking
- ❌ Trusting AI output without validation

