## 📝 Commit Message Format

```
<type>(<scope>): <subject>

<body>

<footer>
```

**Types:**
- `feat`: New feature
- `fix`: Bug fix
- `refactor`: Code restructure (no behavior change)
- `docs`: Documentation only
- `test`: Tests added/modified
- `chore`: Build/tooling changes

**Examples:**
```
feat(budget): implement 3-scenario calculation engine

- Add economico/padrao/premium scenarios
- Integrate SINAPI baseline pricing
- Emit telemetry events for all calculations

Closes ARCH-001
```

```
fix(render): handle fal.ai queue timeout gracefully

Previously crashed on timeout. Now retries up to 3 times
with exponential backoff.
```

